---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — Neon Ninja Run" description="Privacy policy for Neon Ninja Run.">
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: May 8, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-content">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Neon Ninja Run is a game with optional ads, optional in-app purchases, analytics, crash reporting, and Game Center features. We do not sell personal information.</p>
    <h2>Data We Use</h2>
    <p>The app may collect gameplay events, purchase status, ad events, crash diagnostics, device information needed for app reliability, and Game Center achievement or leaderboard progress if you use Game Center.</p>
    <h2>Analytics and Crash Reports</h2>
    <p>We use Firebase Analytics and Firebase Crashlytics to understand important app actions and diagnose crashes. Crash reports may include technical device and app state information.</p>
    <h2>Ads</h2>
    <p>The app may show ads through Google AdMob. Ad providers may use device or advertising data according to their own policies and your device privacy settings.</p>
    <h2>In-App Purchases</h2>
    <p>Purchases are processed by Apple. We receive purchase status needed to unlock items, remove ads, grant currency, or enable premium rewards.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@neonninjarun.com">support@neonninjarun.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
